<br>
My faction with these guys &quot;Couldn't possibly get any worse&quot;, but they're on their own faction, so who cares?<br>
<br>
Canelin. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uliffthemage.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Liff the Mage</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 7<br> <font color=#333333>(10/4/02 1:30:55 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=282.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Dryads</span><hr size=1> Good post Canelin.  I have seen 3 armour drops, crappy stats, but they sell for 74 plat with 114 cha.  There is also lots more of em, just go east a little bit  =). <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ueloinapyromancer.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Eloina Pyromancer</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 45<br> <font color=#333333>(10/4/02 4:37:59 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=282.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Dryads</span><hr size=1> Actually, I've found a number of Beastlords that like the barkleather armor drops.  Arms and leggings seem to be especially well liked.  I've been getting 300-500pp each in the bazaar for these. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=canelin>Canelin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 45<br> <font color=#333333>(10/7/02 4:05:46 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=282.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left clas