<br>
imho for the &quot;danger&quot; involved the loot is pretty good (gems in the 10p range) and the (uncommon rare) armor drops ranging from 40p to 110p each (wrist and chest as samples). it is really safe xp ... just don't try to melee them, they hit hard ... ;-)<br>
<br>
there are 5 or 6 spots with 3 of them and one with 5 spawn points. only one of the 3-group spots doesn't have any wandering locals. and the 5-group spot is very close as well (but it is sort of a highway for wandering locals).<br>
<br>
with KEI and FM i did up to 7 or 8 kills in a row at 54. but after some time you get a balance in how fast you can kill them without too many recoveries. i did a 4 kill cycle most of the time, and sometimes added a 5th one.<br>
<br>
<br>
one more thing, that was said in the other dryads thread: the zone doesn't have more lag than others, but it needs a fast system (especially gfx card). i tried JP with my old P2-350/tnt2 system: almost impossible to move there, used F9 for top view and could move. also my labtop (p3-1100/geforce2-go) can only be used with the top-view. only my desktop system (p3-933/gefroce3-ti5500) is running smooth.<br>
